---
title: Chorizo Arrabiata with Fresh Penne and Parsley
description: Arrabiata can be known to give you a good kick in the pants with its fiery heat, but our version lets you control how spicy you want it! Quick-cooking fresh penne will help get this dish on the dinner table faster than you can say 'buon appetito'!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-arrabiata-au-chorizo-c1877801.jpg
